opennlp.ccg.parse.tagger.io
Class SRILMFactoredBundleCorpusIterator

java.lang.Object
  opennlp.ccg.parse.tagger.io.SRILMFactoredBundleCorpusIterator
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<List<Word>>, Iterator<List<Word>>, CorpusIterator
public class SRILMFactoredBundleCorpusIterator
extends Object
implements CorpusIterator, Iterator<List<Word>>, Iterable<List<Word>>

Assuming an input file of n different sentences of the form: wordbundle1 wordbundle2 ... wordbundleM ... [n-2 lines] wordbundle1 ... wordbundleQ where the 'wordbundle's are SRILM factored LM-compliant bundles of factors (wordform, lemma, POS, supertag, semantic class, etc.). We assume one sentence per line, so the ... bracketing is just a formality (what SRILM expects).
